Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:20.34,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, in East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.01,0:03:24.51,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Three brothers lived together and dreamed of becoming pirates.  { def: tlc, 'a trio' doesn't sound right so went with 'three brothers' }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.31,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Seven years after Sabo's passing, Ace set sail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.81,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Luffy!  I'll be going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:40.90,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And three years after that, Luffy set sail from his hometown, Windmill Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.67,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was first.  Ace was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:47.91,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the third to go, but I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Ace!  I'll catch up to you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:54.80,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And we now return to the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:57.02,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:00.26,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate King?  Yeah, right!
