Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.59,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:52.27,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,It's Garp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.31,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san has returned in a battleship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:55.85,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Is he on official business?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:05.30,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san!  I read the article about the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.30,0:05:07.29,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it was an overwhelming victory for the Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.54,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and I'm glad to see you're all safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:11.08,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,How is Luffy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.56,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen to the world now that Whitebeard is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:15.66,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Garp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:20.77,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,These past few days, we've seen\Na lot of pirate ships on the open sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:25.01,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,They could attack us anytime,\Nit's keeping us awake at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:30.22,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.  I just sank\Nthree of them on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.55,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Really?  What a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:36.62,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,They were just a bunch of amateur pirates\Nwho hadn't even learned how to {i}spell{/i} "Battle". {Literally "Who don't even know the letter "B" in "Battle".}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.71,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,But still, Whitebeard was a deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:44.65,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the world has lost him, the seas are going to be uneasy for a while. {I know the timing may seem odd for this line and the previous... so stab me if you (socky) are not happy with it, stab me -FAb} { def: i rewrote the line to fit the timing }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:49.28,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down just because you live in a remote part of East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:49.92,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:50.53,Main,Marines,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:55.27,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,"Security - Navy HQ Vice-Admiral Garp", huh? { def: tlc, manga has this as 'Guard Station' which reads more naturally.  i'd like to change this "Security Station" (maybe "Security Provided by"?) }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.09,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,That's so reassuring!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.00,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to be afraid of now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.00,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san, we have another problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:08.32,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Bandits came down out of the mountains, and took over Makino's bar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.43,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.44,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!  Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.46,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.85,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:24.33,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some nerve showing your face here again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:27.03,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.65,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:29.86,Main,Marines,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:39.74,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere!  I know this woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:43.95,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:47.26,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You were right there on the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.40,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,They were right there in front of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.58,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,So, what the hell were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.56,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:57.43,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!  Why?!  Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.35,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!  Why, dammit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.28,0:07:10.78,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you just let Ace die like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.74,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Is duty more important than your family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:18.20,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, Garp?!  What kind of hero of the Navy are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.09,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Just die, you damn old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:22.67,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, boss!  Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.33,Main,Bandits,0000,0000,0000,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:27.05,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Garp, say something!  Why didn't you help him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.63,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you prevent it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:31.26,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up.  Get on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:34.47,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You inhuman filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.35,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Dadan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.11,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Makino...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:07.66,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,They were within an arm's reach,\Nyet he was unable to help them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:09.92,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san is suffering the most because of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:21.98,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:25.60,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.55,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:33.78,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's in the most pain... is Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.10,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's get started on today's lesson...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.67,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,How to greet people properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:46.71,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to be working with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:48.96,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That was great, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.48,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.99,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,In times like this, you should say\N"I'm pleased to be working with you."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.95,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What, he got it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.95,0:08:59.76,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The way he said it sounded cool, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.24,0:09:05.37,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, Ace-kun wants to meet\Nthe red-haired captain you're indebted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:10.15,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,We started these lessons because he wants to greet him properly. {and greet him properly... Vegard where did that part go to?!?! Also I had to seperate the line, it was too long -FAb} { def: rewritten }
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.03,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Shanks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:16.20,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! By the time I meet Red-Hair I'll be a pirate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:22.54,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,As a fellow pirate, and as your brother,\Nit's an obvious duty to show him respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:27.18,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Now, try to imagine that he's right here in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:30.49,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ace!  Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:34.30,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzzz.  That's no good.  "Who the hell" is too rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:37.04,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Who're you?!", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.33,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:42.31,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:45.39,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Who are you, you bastard?!", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.30,0:09:47.90,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.31,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.07,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:52.72,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzzz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:55.34,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's "Who is that?", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.36,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,Bzzzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:10:00.66,Flashbacks,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,All wrong.  Are you even trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.79,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,This is all because you keep talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.07,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Quit distracting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:11.78,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ace!  Yesterday, I found the nest of a giant snake, filled with huge eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:13.43,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:15.69,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Huge eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:17.84,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:20.63,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying how to greet people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:24.53,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be in trouble if that huge snake catches me by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:27.89,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be fine if you're with me.  So come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:28.81,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.89,0:10:35.90,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how highly he thought of his brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:45.87,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Makino!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:50.42,Main,Woop Slap,0000,0000,0000,,Garp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:55.97,Main,Woop Slap,0000,0000,0000,,How's Luffy?  The newspapers say they don't know where he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.97,0:10:56.92,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.22,0:11:05.88,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,He escaped in a submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:10.25,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy pursued him with everything they had...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.84,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,and they searched the area thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.84,0:11:15.44,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,But they couldn't find the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:19.49,Main,Garp,0000,0000,0000,,For now, at least he's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.82,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:28.58,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Still, how does Vice-Admiral Garp from Navy HQ\Nand this bandit know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:29.38,Main,Villager,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.71,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is such a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:41.59,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever kind of pirate he becomes, it doesn't matter.  I'm on his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:46.46,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,When I think about how he must be feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:49.02,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,It's like my heart is getting torn in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:12:00.61,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:06.37,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't give in to the pain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:13.70,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we turn far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:18.05,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,to the second half of the Grand Line, The New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.83,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.75,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,How can I thank you for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.84,Main,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:13:00.67,Main,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,He might have been my enemy, but Whitebeard was a pirate worthy of respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.90,Main,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Even Sengoku thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.87,Flashbacks,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard.  Ace. {Copy-paste from 489}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:15.11,Flashbacks,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave their burial to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.77,Flashbacks,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.23,Flashbacks,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,I will take the blame. {End copy-paste from 489}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:26.58,Main,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's time for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.45,Main,Marco,0000,0000,0000,,Sure... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:33.12,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... This must be difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:37.87,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised when I heard about Ace's last actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.80,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Take back what you just said! {Copy-paste from 482}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:45.17,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't make fun of the man who saved my life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.81,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The name of this era is "Whitebeard"!{\i0} {End copy-paste from 482}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:58.65,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,He behaved just like Captain Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:06.65,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,There were times when I wanted the captain to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.18,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,I even wanted him to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.23,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:22.80,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing both victory and defeat, running away and shedding tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.97,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,That is how men grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.05,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for you to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.42,Thoughts,Shanks,0000,0000,0000,,Overcome this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:52.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:59.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:18.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!  I'm so weak!  I can't protect anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.90,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  Damn it!  Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:29.03,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:37.39,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:43.05,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!  Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:48.71,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot do that!  I cannot let you hurt yourself any more than you already have!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.25,0:15:52.93,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,It's my own body!  I can do whatever I want with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:59.68,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then Ace-san's body was his own too.\NHe was free to die, regardless of what we wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.00,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.48,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you say something, I'll beat the crap out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.73,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,If that will make you feel better then go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:13.66,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I'm quite weakened myself, but I will not lose to you.  Not as you are now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.49,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:47.53,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,While I was out chasing Teach...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:54.17,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I met my little brother for the first time in three years, in the Alabasta Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:59.16,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as I saw him, I felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.91,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.30,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!  That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:16.59,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,I said that hurts, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.35,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Can you not see anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:31.85,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The confidence that you'll overcome all obstacles... Your strength, that you've never doubted before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:37.97,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,A horde of enemies ruthlessly shattered your beliefs, and rendered you unable to do a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:40.80,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's your brother, who was your guiding light... { def: shortened to match screen time }
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:43.44,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You have lost so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:48.92,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,The great obstacle known as the world\Nis blocking your vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.30,Flashbacks,Smoker,0000,0000,0000,,You can't defeat me with your ability. {Copy-paste from 468.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:01.51,Flashbacks,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't as reckless as I expected. {Copy-paste from 470.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.94,Flashbacks,Sentoumaru,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:25.16,Flashbacks,Sengoku,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think that I would let you get away? {Copy-paste from 479}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.89,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,As you are now, you cannot see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:44.76,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You're being consumed by dark clouds of regret and self-blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.39,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,It might be hard for you, but Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:50.27,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,You have to defeat those feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.58,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just count everything you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:19:00.16,Main,Jinbe,0000,0000,0000,,What's gone, is gone!\NBut ask yourself this, what remains?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:51.61,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, don't play around up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.17,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You're disrupting my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:01.71,Flashbacks,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, hurry and get everyone into position!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:03.51,Flashbacks,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming!
