Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:17.11,Flashbacks,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, I'm almost done.  Just wait patiently!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:22.33,Flashbacks,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, no matter how badly you get hurt, it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.96,Flashbacks,Chopper,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm gonna fix you up!
