Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.87,Flashbacks,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.87,0:21:15.83,Flashbacks,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.79,Flashbacks,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.77,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,My crew...
