Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:36.72,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!  Nami!  Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.31,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!  Chopper!  Robin!
