Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.75,0:22:24.94,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's caused you guys a lot of trouble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:27.06,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of him for me.{End copy-paste from 457}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.40,0:22:34.58,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I saw that he's no longer the same old Luffy\Nwho'd always chase after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:36.61,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.59,0:22:42.10,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,got a reliable crew of his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.11,0:22:47.05,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, he'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.89,0:22:49.85,Flashbacks,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I was relieved.
